CPlantBox source code

structural/         Plant geometry and growth models (C++ and Python)
                    Includes organs (Root, Stem, Leaf, Seed, GrassLeaf), organism-level
                    classes (Plant, RootSystem, Organism, MappedOrganism), organ parameters,
                    tropism, soil, signed distance functions (sdf), and segment analysis.

functional/         Functional models (C++ and Python)
                    Includes plant hydraulics (PlantHydraulicModel, PlantHydraulicParameters),
                    photosynthesis, phloem flux, perirhizal zone models, exudation,
                    root-soil solute interaction, plant/root conductivities, and
                    van Genuchten soil hydraulic functions.

rsml/               RSML reader and writer (Python)

visualisation/      Visualization related scripts (Python)

tools/              Utility scripts (Python)
                    Includes parameter helper functions.

external/           Third-party libraries and dependencies
                    Includes pybind11, Eigen, tinyxml2, SuiteSparse, SUNDIALS,
                    Gauss-Legendre quadrature, aabbcc, and PiafMunch.

PyPlantBox.cpp      pybind11 bindings exposing the C++ library to Python
__init__.py         Python package entry point

